Minutes to downtown, I-5 & a quick stroll to Cornwall & Squalicum Creek Parks. Inside, find a bright, open living & dining area w/hardwood floors, built-ins & easy flow. The roomy kitchen shines w/granite counters, updated cabinets & tons of storage. Bedrooms feel airy w/tall ceilings & great light. Updated bathroom fts walk-in shower. Mudroom off kitchen opens to dreamy backyard, partially fenced, garden-ready & drenched in sun. A 20x40 heated shop w/power is perfect for woodworking, projects or play & fts a bonus work space. Unfinished basement offers even more room to grow. Eligible for 2 ADUs.

Located in one of Bellingham's most desirable & convenient neighborhoods, Barkley Crossing! This custom one owner home is a hip, newer, 3, 662 square foot contemporary with a fully fenced back yard, fire pit and an awesome sport court. Features include 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, a great room concept with designer fireplace, wood beamed dining room, custom fir cabinetry, chef's kitchen with Thermador appliances, massive rec room, dog wash & two huge decks that overlook acres of trees. Tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac, literally step out your backdoor onto miles of trails. Only a short walk to shopping, restaurants, coffee shops, theaters, & entertainment in Barkley Village. This home offers the utmost in privacy from nearly every room!

Check out this spacious and affordable 3 bedroom/1.75 bathroom home only minutes to downtown Ferndale. Open concept floor plan, with lots of natural light, storage and a very functional layout. There is a separate laundry room, deck off the kitchen, covered parking and garden shed. Oversized Primary bedroom has an ensuite and huge walk-in closet! This home will need some cosmetic upgrade and offers a fantastic opportunity to personalize your space and build equity. So many possibilities! Ferndale Estates is clean, well-managed and one of the nicest parks in Whatcom County. No age restriction but homes must be owner occupied. Dues include water/septic. Close to shopping/parks and walking trails.
